sentences: Catherine Elisabeth Britt (born 31 December 1984) is an Australian country music artist who has had success in both her native Australia and in the United States.
She started her career in Newcastle in 1999, she moved to Nashville from 2002 to 2008 and then returned to Australia.

Britt has had three singles in top 40 on the US Billboard Hot Country Songs charts with "The Upside of Being Down", her highest, peaking at No. 36 in 2004.
